# Dashboard Update Plan

## Goal Description
Fix the layout matching the uploaded pictures, and add new specific breaking news sources (Sky News Arabia, Alarabiya, specific Twitter accounts, and a new Telegram channel), along with their custom logos.

## Proposed Changes

### Configuration
#### [MODIFY] [grid.js](file:///c:/Users/abady/Downloads/%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%B3%20%D9%85%D8%B1%D9%82%D8%A7%D8%A8/src/grid.js)
- Update `widgetDefs` with exact coordinates matching the screenshots:
  - `live-tv`: `w: 4`, `h: 4`
  - `gold-silver`: `x: 4`, `y: 0`, `w: 3`, `h: 2`
  - `market-overview`: `x: 4`, `y: 2`, `w: 3`, `h: 2`
  - `world-clock`: `x: 7`, `y: 0`, `w: 2`, `h: 4`
  - `breaking-news`: `x: 9`, `y: 0`, `w: 3`, `h: 4`

### Proxy Updates
#### [MODIFY] [proxy.js](file:///c:/Users/abady/Downloads/%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%B3%20%D9%85%D8%B1%D9%82%D8%A7%D8%A8/proxy.js)
- Build a new `/alarabiya` scraping endpoint to hit `https://www.alarabiya.net/breaking-news` (extracting `.item-title` and `<time>`).
- Build a new `/skynews` endpoint to hit `https://www.skynewsarabia.com/breaking-news-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D8%AE%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B1-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B9%D8%A7%D8%AC%D9%84%D8%A9` or its RSS feed.

### Frontend Widget Updates
#### [MODIFY] [breaking-news.js](file:///c:/Users/abady/Downloads/%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%B3%20%D9%85%D8%B1%D9%82%D8%A7%D8%A8/src/widgets/breaking-news.js)
- Override the hardcoded sources:
