## Verification Plan
### Automated Tests
- Restart [proxy.js](file:///c:/Users/abady/Downloads/%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%B3%20%D9%85%D8%B1%D9%82%D8%A7%D8%A8/proxy.js) and test endpoints locally using browser or `curl`.
- Send a request to `/alarabiya` and `/skynews` checking if 200 OK and valid JSON array is returned.

### Manual Verification
- User will review the live dashboard at port 8080 to visually verify:
  1. The new layout matches the 4-column structure (Live TV, Gold+Market, Clock, News).
  2. Breaking news entries populate with custom logos (Sky News Arabia, Alarabiya, Aljazeera, Twitter account avatars).
  3. The proxy successfully provides background feed polling.
